link: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/visualstudio/install/create-an-offline-installation-of-visual-studio?view=vs-2022

STEP 1: DOWNLOAD BOOTSTRAPPER
STEP 2: MOVE STRAPPER TO DRIVE C
STEP 3: OPEN CMD FROM THIS SAME LOCATION.
STEP 4: RUN THE CODE BELOW FOR VS MOBILE DEVELOPMENT WITH C++
vs_Community.exe --layout c:\localVSlayout --add Microsoft.VisualStudio.Workload.NativeDesktop --includeRecommended --lang en-US


NB: YOU CAN ADD OTHER FEATURES OR COMPONENTS